f optical brightness variations therefore allows a\ndetermination of the surface gravity with a precision of <25 percent for\ninactive Sun-like stars at main-sequence to giant stages of evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Aug 2013 22:23:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
