 time as\nthe ARR and point to changes in trial characteristics over the years,\nquestioning comparisons between historical and recent trials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2013 11:36:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2013 15:55:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 May 2015 11:29:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-03"}
